Package org.lemming.interfaces

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Element
    This interface sets a boolean that is checkable by all inherited objects
    Frame<T>
    Frame holds an 2D image plus some useful metadata.
    LocalizationInterface
    The basic interface for holding a localization following the ViSP standard
    ModuleInterface
    Interface for all modules, inspired by the org.scijava.module interface
    PluginInterface
    Interface for Plug-ins which are registered by the SciJava Framework
    Store
    A structure delivering data on a queue
